## Image inventory

### Demo files (`public/demos/real-estate-intelligence-center/`)
- No `<img>` tags anywhere in `index.html`, `app.js`, `shell.js`, `output-queue.js`, `intel-brief.js`, `engines/*.js`, or any other JS module.
- No `url()` references in `styles.css`.
- No image assets (PNG/JPG/SVG/GIF/WebP) in the demo directory.

**Result: zero images to QA in the demo itself. All visual content is rendered via HTML/CSS (SVG icons inlined as text/emoji, colored divs, CSS gradients). No broken, miscropped, or wrong images possible.**

